\">人既話可以點自辨?</span>"},{"pid":"4d6a084dec340add151ac2d6284f6172652bd913","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:12.000Z","msg":"自推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef1c078773c8145ce7cbfba8cadfa125bf86c37","tid":1467211,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:46.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"9424543a7c54f8962b7de4d47b115a844af3b145","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c7dfc08ae0c0639bc4585c8f223a0335360b55d","tid":1467211,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"568c1d72f40cd8039c90767ae7f75de26b8abb91","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:28.000Z","msg":"而家出面好多留言帶風向<br />\n熱門po全部屌勇武/機場輸哂/叫人停機場活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你信，咁政府就不費一兵一卒，不費一粒子彈就瓦解機場和理飛</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 不分化不割蓆<br />\n一捉到嗰個姓符既疑似公安之後，突然間好多人開po屌手足，又話破壞哂今日和理飛、 勇武變黑、勇武有勇無謀之類。意圖好明顯，想分化，想話勇武派破壞左和理非今日活動得到嘅成果。 <br />\n<br />\n2. 捉鬼處理手法<br />\n自從811後，大家變得好敏感，覺得身邊好多鬼，係！好！正！常！但係，大家要諗清楚到底捉鬼後既處理手法，係衝上前綁住佢既時間，會唔會比時間佢解釋/出示任何證明自己身份既野？  <br />\n<br />\n發現真係鬼後，五花大綁後我地可以點處理？ <br />\n如果我地綁住佢，圍住佢之後可以點？黑警都唔敢係國際機場行私刑，我地更加唔做得。<br />\n<br />\n其實影哂佢個樣，影哂證件，推佢離開機場，比記者寫新聞已經足夠。你又唔會打死佢，但又比記者影到衝突場面，咁樣好蝕底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 疑似好多鬼帶頭衝<br />\n我相信大家既目標都係五大訴求，同時同意左機場係和理非活動。 一旦發生衝突/捉鬼事件，前面一定會有鬼滲入，或者有手足會比較激動，咁樣係好正常！ 求下後面和理非一定大聲嗌 「冷靜」 「退後」 ，比d空間前面，同時抒緩下當時既氣氛，冷靜下諗下發生咩事，下一步點做。<br />\n<br />\n今日，有廿個黑警無啦啦行入機場，然後拉咗手足，再舉槍，令到現場手足好激動，包括我。 跟住好快就話捉到鬼，發生左一連串大家都認為係個局嘅事件。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以，後排有人一齊大嗌冷靜係好重要</span><br />\n<br />\n利伸係現場，咪屌我冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化，不割蓆</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場和你飛，一定要繼續落去</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以比林奠不費一兵一卒，不費一粒子彈就瓦解機場和理飛</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:03.000Z","msg":"如果佢只係得張身份証，點証明佢係人定鬼? <span style=\"color: red;\">人既話可以點自辨?</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:25:31.000Z","msg":"係，無錯。<br />\n除非係佢身上搜到委任證或者係公安嘅證明文件，如果唔係根本無辦法肯定佢就係鬼。 但好明顯佢哋做得鬼一定唔會將呢啲嘢放喺身上面，所以結論係唔好嘥時間捉鬼，除非佢專登挑起事端打人，否則捉黎都係嘥時間，你又唔會捉得晒。"},{"pid":"177d1031c820254314b0cb99dd2e4b4338066230","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:10.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081f891eb7c4133b10c57a6fee25af0632562176","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:22.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91df8fa55a89cbd4fededa5b3eda48419ddde9c9","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95f8298220c98c9a4ec3f00ac502eda31481d7c","tid":1467211,"uid":72800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化</span> 保持警覺</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心暗黑兵法劇本：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n內耗：內部分化示威者、<br />\n酷刑威嚇被捕人士、<br />\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、<br />\n逐步暴力鎮壓 拘捕前線瓦解、<br />\n文宣抹黑 嫁禍 插贜示威者、<br />\n暗殺第一滴血 逆轉民意 國際譴責、<br />\n人民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、<br />\n中立派賺錢派 政治疲勞、<br />\n鼓吹經濟下滑 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、<br />\n拖延分散擊破 學季始開、<br />\n雨傘結局  清算開始<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">十項推文 試著說<br />\n勿忘612、721、811</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">811警暴連環<br />\n⒈蓄意謀殺女救護 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>布袋鉛彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>瞄準</strong></span>眼球 永久失明 面骨碎裂、<br />\n⒉插贜竹枝 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">造偽證</span></strong> 誣陷被捕者、<br />\n⒊地鐡<strong>站內 水平發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣、<br />\n⒋警<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">喬裝示威者 發動衝擊</span></strong>縱火、<br />\n⒌普通話<strong>軍人 多處滲透</strong>武統、<br />\n⒍<strong>一米內行刑 掃射</strong>胡椒彈槍、險釀電梯<strong>人踩人</strong>、<br />\n⒎<strong>縱容黑幫</strong>橫行 毆打記者路人、<br />\n⒏濫暴<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">痛毆 重創被捕者</span></strong> 打掉門牙 血肉模糊、<br />\n⒐屋村<strong>老人民居 發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣<br />\n１０. 殘害救護員、<strong>救護舉旗警告</strong> 尖沙咀<strong>阻礙救援</strong> 違反國際人道法 屬嚴重刑事罪行</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">August 11, 2019 *** Police Brutality ***<br />\n<br />\n⒈ <strong>Macilously and unlawfully</strong> cause <strong>Greivous Bodily Harm</strong> - Gun <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Aims for the head</strong></span>: <br />\n    <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Shooting lean-filled pellet round directly to a First-aider&rsquo;s eye</strong></span>, causing grievous bodily harm including:<br />\n<strong>      - Right eyeball RUPTURED. <br />\n      - Permanent BLINDNESS. <br />\n      - Eyelids &amp; tear ducts LACERATIONS.<br />\n      - Facial FRACTURED.</strong><br />\n⒉ <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Planting fake evidence</span></strong> on arrested protesters (putting sharp bamboo into protestors&rsquo; bag)<br />\n⒊ <strong>Unlawfully &amp; Horizontally lauching TEARGAS canisters INDOOR</strong> (in MTR subway stations at civilians)<br />\n⒋ Officers <strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">disguised as demonstrators to take the lead</span></strong>, and incite them to violence.<br />\n⒌ Mandarin-speaking officers spotted: suspected to be <strong>Mainland China officers undercovering</strong> as HKPF.<br />\n⒍ <strong>SWEEP-SHOTTING protesters with projectiles</strong> (Pepperball Pistol) at less than 1m range. <br />\n     Shoved protesters down escalators (almost causing <strong>STAMPEDE</strong>).<br />\n⒎ <strong>Turned a blind eye towards gangsters</strong>(who support HK police) chasing up <br />\n     and <strong>beating pedestrians</strong>, reporters and protesters on streets.<br />\n⒏ Bloody arrest: <strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Brutally beaten up arrested protester</span></strong> (protester who was under control - wrestled to the ground moaning in pain with front tooth knocked out).<br />\n⒐ <strong>Launching TEARGAS canisters</strong> in suburban area populated by old <strong>residential buildings</strong>(outside the <strong>elderly homes</strong>, community centers, and nearby residences).<br />\n１０. (Serious Criminal Offence) <strong>Obstruction of medical care</strong> - in violation of the International Humanitarian Law. <strong>First-aider raising the Flag for Warning</strong> in TST.<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"552abd7b7836720003e16adc414258eba2d6a3f9","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26030b0d322b319cda561f9964925900672de7f1","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:28.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac21e8955fbd886858fc2679b0274ea034bc1fa","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb0ba6fb205e4500d192462ba3e2a2680cf3463","tid":1467211,"uid":263366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:38:06.000Z","msg":"推！！！事後檢討好重要！！"},{"pid":"997a8631ba65e917610f5feb5f01c1e7ef789b95","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:41:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中央已出手，所有分化po請善用不推文回覆，叫人唔好再推，停止再將佢推上熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔可以比林奠不費一兵一卒，不費一粒子彈就瓦解機場和理飛"},{"pid":"0581eb700a59cc76fdfa7b7271edc043c9ba668d","tid":1467211,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0